INSERT INTO COMMENT(COMMENT_ISSUE_URL,COMMENT_ID,COMMENT_USER_NAME,COMMENT_USER_ID,COMMENT_CREATE_TIME,COMMENT_UPDATE_TIME,COMMENT_DESC) values ('https://api.github.com/repos/cleebp/csc-510-group-g/issues/1','171416434','reachspirit','16613192','2016-01-13T20:02:32Z','2016-01-13T20:02:32Z','Here are some papers on code cloning. It turns out that code clone is quite different from our goal of an efficient clipboard manager. 
Clone management: Clone analysis tool with tag cloud visualization. Jump to the picture. It gives a description of the procedure of clone management.
